ouzandeh]]\n | minister2_termstart   = 27 May 2012\n | minister2_termend     = 1 September 2013\n | minister2_party       = Society of Devotees of the Islamic Revolution\n}}\n{{Cabinet table minister\n | title                 = [[Administrative and Recruitment Affairs Organization|Management Development and<br>Human Resources Vice President]]\n | minister1             = [[Lotfollah Forouzandeh]]\n | minister1_termstart   = 25 October 2009\n | minister1_termend     = 27 May 2012\n | minister1_party       = Society of Devotees of the Islamic Revolution\n | minister1_ref         = <ref>{{cite web|title=Appointment of Vice President for Management Development and Human Resources|url=http://www.hamshahrionline.ir/details/93640/Iran/estate|publisher=[[Hamshahri|Hamshahri Online]]|accessdate=16 December 2017|language=Persian|date=25 October 2009}}</ref>\n\n | minister2             = [[Ebrahim Azizi]]\n | minister2_termstart   = 27 May 2012\n | minister2_termend     = 26 December 2012\n | minister2_party       = Nonpartisan\n\n | minister3             = [[Gholam-Hossein Elham]]\n | minister3_termstart   = 26 December 2012\n | minister3_termend     = 3 August 2013\n | minister3_party       = Front of Islamic Revolution Stability\n}}\n{{Cabinet table minister\n | title                 = Legal Affairs Vice President\n | minister1             = [[Fatemeh Bodaghi]]\n | minister1_termstart   = 30 November 2009\n | minister1_termend     = 11 August 2013\n | minister1_party       = Nonpartisan\n | minister1_ref         = <ref>{{cite web|title=Fatemeh Bodaghi Appointed as Vice President for Legal Affairs|url=http://www.hamshahrionline.ir/details/96310/Iran/estate|publisher=[[Hamshahri|Hamshahri Online]]|accessdate=16 December 2017|language=Persian|date=30 November 2009}}</ref>\n}}\n{{Cabinet table minister\n | title                 = [[Foundation of Martyrs and Veterans Affairs|Martyrs Vice President]]\n | minister1             = [[Masoud Zaribafan]]\n | minister1_termstart   = 17 J